resources.string: FISE v2 Concierge: Made by Calin Hadarean, Ernest Nkansah-Badu and Mohammad Ali Syed

Connect with your admin by entering your three registration codes on the \'Register\' page. You will then be able to see your history and call your Gp, Dentist and Optometrist. For more help, see some of the commands you can use below.
Weather \nSay: \'What is the weather like in London today?\'
Stocks \nSay: \'What is the stock value of IBM?\'
Search Recipe by Name \nSay: \'Tell me a recipe for Ramen\'
Search Recipe by Ingredient \nSay: \'Tell me a recipe using fish\'
Search for Random Recipe \nSay: \'Tell me a recipe\'
Read Out a Recipe \nFirst search for a recipe eg \'Tell me a recipe for Ramen\'. Then say: \'Read out that recipe\'
Search for a Charity \nSay: \'Tell me about the charity Oxfam\'
Search for a Charity by Location \nSay: \'Give me the name of a charity in Liverpool\'
Nearest Bus/Train Station \nSay: \'Tell me where the nearest train station is\'
Search for Specific Bus Stop/Train Station \nSay: \'Tell me where Euston train station is\'
Search for a Book by Name \nSay: \'Tell me about the book Frankenstein\'
Search for a Book by Category \nSay: \'Tell me about a Romance book\'
Open a Book \n First search for a book eg \'Tell me about the book Frankenstein\'. Then say: \'Open that book\'
News \nSay: \'Tell me news about Boris Johnson\'
Dictionary \nSay: \'What does the word sunshine mean?\'
Air Quality \nSay: \'What is the air quality in London?\'
Open an app on your phone \nSay: \'Open YouTube\'
Navigate Concierge App \nSay: \'Go to the History page\'
Search for items online \nSay: \'Search Amazon for Jam\'
